at inabot ako.

485
00:31:08,770 --> 00:31:09,980
Magandang bagay iyan.

486
00:31:12,990 --> 00:31:13,880
Pagkatapos...

487
00:31:14,850 --> 00:31:16,720
Aalis ka na naman ba?

488
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:20,310
Sa totoo lang, ang tagal ko nang nandito

489
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:22,760
parang robot vacuum

