497
00:31:41,140 --> 00:31:42,400
Susuportahan kita habangbuhay.

498
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:44,380
Ikaw ang aking sandigan.

499
00:31:47,320 --> 00:31:48,770
Walang sinuman ang pinapayagang tumakas.

500
00:31:48,770 --> 00:31:49,710
Kailangan nandito ka,

501
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:51,240
